# Normalize line endings in the repo. Critical for the shell script: a Windows
# clone with core.autocrlf=true would otherwise rewrite serve_report.sh to CRLF,
# which Git Bash cannot execute (`\r` errors). Force LF for code on checkout.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf
*.py text eol=lf
*.ps1 text eol=lf

# Binary assets — never touch.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.gif binary
